    Pretty much. He is half-dead like Ben was and his surviving Noise is observing the world also like Ben. It shows at the end of one of the short storie<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Pretty much. He is half-dead like Ben was and his surviving Noise is observing the world also like Ben. It shows at the end of one of the short stories (the one included with newer copies of MoM) that he eventually wakes up. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
