<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1698332-what-i-don-t-understand-is-how-lee-can">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[What I don't understand is how Lee can "see" through Wilf's noise. What it sounds like is being described are the pictures that go along with noise, kind of like the way the Spackle communicate. But if he's blind, he shouldn't be able to see those pictures. Does it just mean he can hear Wilf's noise? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
