        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer718447555" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17652574514792089806"><u>Star Rating</u>: <i>—&gt;</i> <b>5 Stars</b><br/><br/>RE-READ DEC. 31st, 2020- 5 stars once again. This series holds such a special place in my heart!!!!<br/><br/>__________________<br/><br/>Angharrad owns my heart. 💙<br/><br/>love<br/>boy colt</span>

